Create Procedure dbo.UpsertDimProcedureCategories
AS
BEGIN

Update 
ld
SET
  ProcedureCategoryCode= ld.ProcedureCategoryCode
, ProcedureCategoryDesc= ld.ProcedureCategoryDesc
FROM
Load.ProcedureCategories ld
INNEr JOIN dbo.DimProcedureCategories dp ON ld.ProcedureCategoryId = dp.ProcedureCategoryId

INSERT INTO dbo.DimProcedureCategories
(
	ProcedureCategoryId
,	ProcedureCategoryCode
,	ProcedureCategoryDesc
)
SELECT
	ld.ProcedureCategoryId
,	ld.ProcedureCategoryCode
,	ld.ProcedureCategoryDesc
FROM
Load.ProcedureCategories ld
LEFT JOIN dbo.DimProcedureCategories dp ON ld.ProcedureCategoryId = dp.ProcedureCategoryId
WHERE dp.ProcedureCategoryId IS NULL

END
GO
